evilalarm (0.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * Show previously used alarms
  * Add option to prevent device lock (no need to remember the lock code first thing in the morning)
  * Fix snooze with blubbels module
  * Prevent creation of multiple settings windows
  * Minor UI improvements

